{"tid":2006454,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"想開間黃店電器舖。。。","createTime":"2020-05-07T18:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T10:00:15.000Z","uid":40466,"like":79,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9b42ec439de437796aa8b721195efba6125ab792","tid":2006454,"uid":40466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T18:56:14.000Z","msg":"一直想接手屋企生意 但畢業無耐就返緊其他工學下野<br />\n成日見到有人問有無黃既電器鋪<br />\n但聽屋企人講行內就無啦 所以好想自己自立門戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企兩老小藍 門市唔可以貼文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢地話如果我上網自己做就鐘意點就點<br />\n但我地裝機師傅都黃<br />\n<br />\n所以如果有意可以係留言問價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思要上黎r生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔想成日比兩老睇死 覺得黃係小眾<br />\n好想自立門戶 成功有一間黃既電器舖再請返手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3901dc274d636587014ef62fae09efce362ba0dd","tid":2006454,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"規模幾大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d71c9277cfefa0ed567c4462b74d4b683791efc","tid":2006454,"uid":40466,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3901dc274d636587014ef62fae09efce362ba0dd","tid":2006454,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T18:57:55.000Z","msg":"規模幾大？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:00:15.000Z","msg":"其實一直有門市開左廿幾年<br />\n只係如果我有成績就可以說服兩老退休/自立門戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想開一至兩間分店 主要接工程"},{"pid":"7edfa03ad9e10cc05f84a7af517fe47df7faf3f9","tid":2006454,"uid":199670,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T19:01:29.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n如果有人做埋裝修就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b642